{"tid":1683004,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[二創填詞]不屈進行曲 榮光填詞(歌名暫時:榮光進行曲) 有一句未填 幫幫忙呀","createTime":"2019-10-30T11:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T02:49:32.000Z","uid":200873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc796bb249300a412e8ad1d4e784fca0b3b45e6","tid":1683004,"uid":200873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"我就不詳細說我是誰啦(其實我本想申請連登 不過台灣好像無法 這是我友人帳號)<br />\n這次是不屈進行曲的填詞阿 不過還有一句沒有填上 大家來幫幫忙阿<br />\n註:這次也是台語 不過幫我用廣東話填上也可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正式版出來會有粵語歌詞(這個帳號的主人要幫我弄)<br />\n<br />\n來抗爭(阿) 上街吧<br />\n土地上 榮光退去<br />\n抗爭人們 大街頂懸<br />\n絕望矜住 抗爭 力量<br />\n<br />\n在煙霧中 你驚惶嗎<br />\n是眾人裡 熱血直流<br />\n向前過程 總有犧牲<br />\n建自由 光輝的 香港<br />\n<br />\n願榮光 能返來這香港<br />\n義勇軍 和重光 成過去<br />\n記著 現此時應該 進前<br />\n<br />\n這光輝 猶依在大地上<br />\n讓民主 和自由久長流<br />\n____________________&larr;這裡要填 廣東話也可<br />\n將榮光 歸人中<br />\n<br />\n矜:撐<br />\n人中:人們(即是各位 正在抗爭的各位)<br />\n頂懸:上 「街上」、「世上」<br />\n義勇軍:皇家香港軍團(港英時代) <a href=\"https://ppt.cc/fgKSkx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fppt.cc%2FfgKSkx&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=fcdeb5b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ppt.cc/fgKSkx</a><br />\n重光:香港重光紀念日 <a href=\"https://ppt.cc/fR8S3x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fppt.cc%2FfR8S3x&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=f8b45815\" target=\"_blank\">https://ppt.cc/fR8S3x</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n猶:仍舊、還<br />\n《論語．微子》：「往者不可諫，來者猶可追。」<br />\n<br />\n依:情況沒改變<br />\n唐．方干〈獻王大夫〉詩二首之二：「歷任聖朝清峻地，至今依是少年身。」"},{"pid":"3c1c85a1e1c9f912f80e19d2d8f22da7081c8241","tid":1683004,"uid":200873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293be194f8672ebd8d3d906711ea728c59c89eeb","tid":1683004,"uid":200873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家幫幫我呀"},{"pid":"7b4fc4ad47c4050d3fbf6ef03850ba62dbf7f709","tid":1683004,"uid":151178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"輕輕推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2d1fd2bc6bfae66e8bd77faa6123c84f72fc59","tid":1683004,"uid":284860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89969f6808bc33378e6b9d13ace469b0c3359a3c","tid":1683004,"uid":200873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"19cec1e3b3650fe95dcce7699ed30bc56640c9ff","tid":1683004,"uid":8521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a2b8a32276c174a23cc423ff2522fc8ba74e492a","tid":1683004,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:49:32.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}